OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a cloudy day with
OL,6,Frain at times across the west. Staying
OL,7,Fdrier in the east although patchy rain
OL,8,Fat times here too, especially in the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FStaying quite cloudy through
OL,12,Fthe evening and overnight with some
OL,13,Fshowery rain. Some drier and clearer
OL,14,Fspells developing towards morning.
OL,15,FWindy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
