OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA mostly dry start with some
OL,6,Fbright spells. Rain spreads in from
OL,7,Fthe west through the morning,
OL,8,Foccasionally heavy. Drier in east.
OL,9,FClear spells and showers in evening.
OL,10,FBreezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry
OL,13,Fstart Friday but chance of rain for a
OL,14,Ftime in the middle of the day. Dry and
OL,15,Fbright for most of Saturday, rain
OL,16,Flater. Cloudy, breezy, patchy rain
OL,17,FSunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
